channel.description: So i've been coding 317 Pi for quit a while, and my friends want me to create a 614/659 pk server as like a world 2... and when i run the source up this is what it says. [code][RS2Server] Loading Cache... [Cache] Fully loaded cache. [RS2Server] Loading Incarnation... [PacketManager] Loading packet handlers... [PacketManager] Loaded 44 packet handlers. [ClanManager] Loading clans.... [ClanManager] Loaded 35 clans. [AreaManager] Loading areas... [AreaManager] Loaded 7 areas. [NPCDropLoader] Loading drops... [NPCDropLoader] Loaded 8 drops [MagicHandler] Loading spells... [MagicHandler] Loaded 46 spells. [ItemDefinition] Loading item definitions... [ItemDefinition] Loaded 20175 item definitions. [NPCDefinition] Loading npc definitions... [NPCDefinition] Loaded 17 npc definitions. [NPCLoader] Loading default npc spawns... [Region] Could not find map [m32_30] [NPCLoader] Loaded 87 default npc spawns. [ShopManager] Loaded Shops [RS2Server] Binding server... [ChannelBinder] Server bound to port - 43594 [Region] Could not find map [m31_29] [Region] Could not find map [m46_76] [/code] And it'll continue looking for more maps but can't find it. I have 0 experience with 614+ but i'm sure i'll get the hang of it soon, just need a little help beginning.
